				<td valign="top">
					<div align="left">
</b>
						<p><font face = arial color = "#009933"><b><a class = navy style="text-decoration:none" href="http://www.genomecurator.org/ORFcurator/ORFc_index.html">About ORFcurator</a></b></p></font>
						<p><font face = arial><a class = blueBlackGray  style="text-decoration:none" href="http://www.genomecurator.org/ORFcurator/ORFc_database.html">About the Database Sequences</a></p></font>
						<p><font face = arial><a class = blueBlackGray  style="text-decoration:none" href="http://www.genomecurator.org/ORFcurator/ORFc_pubs.html">Relevant Publications</a></p></font>
						<p><font face = arial><a class = blueBlackGray  style="text-decoration:none" href="http://www.genomecurator.org/ORFcurator/ORFc_download.html">Download</a></p></font>
						<p><font face = arial><a class = blueBlackGray  style="text-decoration:none" href="http://www.genomecurator.org/ORFcurator/ORFc_contact.html">Contact Information</a></p></font>
						<p><font face = arial><a class = blueBlackGray  style="text-decoration:none" target=help href="http://www.genomecurator.org/ORFcurator/help/ORFc_help.html">Help</a></p></font>
					</div>
